name: Qt Phrase Books File
summary: Learn about .QPH files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: QPH files may also be generated from Qt Translation Source files (.TS files) using the lconvert utility, which is included with the Qt SDK.
NOTE: Qt SDK was previously developed by Nokia and Digia.

description: Language translation file created by Qt Linguist, a program used for translating and internationalizing Qt (pronounced "Cute") applications; contains text phrases and their translations into another language; provides a translation repository that can be used by multiple Qt applications.
